imdb.plot outline: A 'Docuality' series of the unbelieveable underwater world of scuba divers above and below the surface. Gruesome & amazing stories told by featured divers and actors, then to be reinacted by the accredited worldwide technical dive agency UTD...and the insanity of the life of Andrew Georgitsis & his team. There is much much more to this series, stay tuned...
